## üèóÔ∏è Architecture

### Data Flow
```
Admin/Ops ‚Üí Airtable (WRITE) ‚îÄsync‚Üí Supabase (READ) ‚Üê Application
```

**Important Rules**:
- ‚úÖ Application READS from Supabase only
- ‚úÖ Admin/Ops WRITES to Airtable only
- ‚úÖ Sync is automatic and bidirectional

### Authentication
- Provider: Supabase Auth
- Methods: Email/Password (+ OAuth if implemented)
- Protected routes: Use ProtectedRoute HOC

---

## üíª Technical Constraints

### Language & Framework
- **TypeScript**: Strict mode enabled
- **React**: 18+ with functional components only
- **Build tool**: Vite
- **Package manager**: npm

### Code Style
- **Components**: Functional components with hooks
- **State management**: Zustand (or Context API)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS (no inline styles)
- **Formatting**: Prettier + ESLint

### File Naming
- Components: PascalCase (`UserCard.tsx`)
- Utilities: camelCase (`formatDate.ts`)
- Pages: PascalCase (`Dashboard.tsx`)
- Types: PascalCase (`User.ts`)

